IN RE: Olander R. BYNUM 109P17-4 Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 9, 2018

Mr. Olander R. Bynum, For Bynum, Olander R.

Mr. Joseph Finarelli, Special Deputy Attorney General, Mr. Ben R. David, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 21st of March 2018 by Petitioner for Petition for Rehearing:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 9th of May 2018."
